{"tid":1183134,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以婉轉話比男友知我唔開心","createTime":"2019-06-02T16:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T18:40:50.000Z","uid":67037,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e645db11bf706238530247b4c766e28f29d61780","tid":1183134,"uid":67037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"一齊左6年幾，最近感覺佢對我愈來愈冷淡，以前佢成日主動揾我報告行踪，食飯痾屎乜都講，但依加開始覺得我煩，打電話比佢facetime佢都會唔想理我，有時會直頭講埋出黎唔鐘意facetime，語氣好差咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又成日鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道佢唔會係出軌個啲人，佢應該仲係愛我嘅，我亦都有向佢講過我有啲唔開心，但講完之後佢又好似冇咩反應咁，依舊好似以前咁冷淡，出街拍拖就好似例行公事咁，而我就變得可有可無咁，究竟點樣令可以比佢知我真係好唔開心<br />\n男朋友啊，我愛你先會想痴住你，唔好成日將我推開好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0808bbbc73cbd228a1330d24bbaec06ed0bed6","tid":1183134,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:51:16.000Z","msg":"唔畀佢含"},{"pid":"3024811d481179fcb7bb681f201ef0a8ccaa7dc4","tid":1183134,"uid":3553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"淡左變左心，好難搞"},{"pid":"7751b82b62d46f6ebd56c7cc53d6f47948ee8f55","tid":1183134,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:51:54.000Z","msg":"同佢講 無事"},{"pid":"fe33039ba3c32c78c40602188e94b109c85b3c6f","tid":1183134,"uid":82500,"like"