oji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"一齊咗六年感情已經好穩定，唔可以話係平淡嘅<br />\n佢唔鍾意FaceTime 會唔會因為工作好攰，或者有同事朋友喺隔離唔方便呢？<br />\n<br />\n我同我女朋友一齊咗三個月，都開始好似你咁，因為佢做嘢好忙，所以依家得我一個主動搵吓佢，係有少少灰心嘅，但過多個月佢就得閒返。<br />\n<br />\n所以有時候係時間問題啫，唔鍾意嘅絕對一齊唔到咁耐，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f374d7759d73b1c64f8db09cfa6e7ea87ccdd12","tid":1183134,"uid":67037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"125d7ca7671e4dd4d5eab4a8ba09b39b210fc3e2","tid":1183134,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00113fb4a179af3027534e4b09cbc1914182caf1","tid":1183134,"uid":67037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a956887259d8f605bc89cb626736264c48908a2f","tid":1183134,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"佢體諒呀，但都會覺得我好似已經對佢無咩興趣/頹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:27:05.000Z","msg":"有冇表達你愛佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:30:22.000Z","msg":"seldom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔太識 本身份人木獨 叫我搞笑都仲ok 叫我表達愛就唔太識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:36:57.000Z","msg":"最親嘅人有咩表達唔到，多啲讚下佢，主動拖佢隻手，記得佢講過嘅野，有機會買啲小禮物送比佢已經好開心"},{"pid":"b005f137d89d45e9ac677ac66e0e1e81bab65cfd","tid":1183134,"uid":119667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"986558d91eb98bb2cef735b01404bc9b3b5c8fe5","tid":1183134,"uid":67037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b6d5ed2609302bc974cb9189fabb92c13493a68","tid":1183134,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eda3340a65c2e16d4f0952231112c86dff8331c","tid":1183134,"uid":67037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"好似我個個咁，會成日鬧我但好少讚我哄我，真係會令我自信心好低落，覺得自己冇樣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:29:21.000Z","msg